{"tid":1603424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[求幫推] 10.1全部人自備打火機同印一支黨旗","createTime":"2019-09-29T16:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T20:12:44.000Z","uid":86363,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b783b8bca7e8a17d37711966e5422bdad80eb0b1","tid":1603424,"uid":86363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:25:47.000Z","msg":"有留意今日嘅都知<br />\n依家要100%和理非已經無可能<br />\n啲狗根本亂鳩咁嚟<br />\n但咁樣只會令媒體失焦<br />\ne.g. 八五無人講罷工，美領變講破壞中環站<br />\n所以無論十一係港島定五區<br />\n我哋依家最需要嘅<br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\">做一樣比警暴更有impact嘅事</span><br />\n令傳媒聚焦番落賀佢老母<br />\n<br />\n前幾日有人提議全民燒黨旗<br />\n個人覺得不失為一個好方法<br />\n但集合連登嘅智慧同創意<br />\n我相信可以送習大大一份更大嘅賀禮<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<br />\n求幫推"},{"pid":"afa35887ec0f7ae9a6c22e246faf25042df174ba","tid":1603424,"uid":86363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"07c27ed4cc9b0aa7cd50806bd27c77f60671966e","tid":1603424,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:26:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42641a22419c17f5741e99cfd1ea537526054bd5","tid":1603424,"uid":86363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:26:46.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"7dfbbe3733973b4eaa7898411b53a364d8dbeec4","tid":1603424,"uid":86363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:27:03.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"d78ce313ea13bc8616cbe1eb4ceb6754226eed3d","tid":1603424,"uid":86363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:27:17.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"9efbb57071e2804c9b04bec694ccfa89394fcfd4","tid":1603424,"uid":86363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:27:33.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"30fe03ad6db710a8e86a539283d6a3b0bddec231","tid":1603424,"uid":86363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:27:48.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"3aa0237207d770a119dee57330e5fae84007b146","tid":1603424,"uid":86363,"l